<div>
  <p>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Welcome to Trade Campus Books where UMass Amherst students can list, send offers, and make deals on books they wish to buy and sell. All users require a '@student.umass.edu' email address to become verified. Only verified users can list books they want to buy or sell, send offers regarding a currently listed book, or accept an offer to make a deal on a book. This site is <strong>completely free</strong> and will remain so forever. If you have any questions, feel free to email us at <%= mail_to 'support@tradecampusbooks.com' %>. To begin, <%= link_to 'sign up', signup_path %> or start <%= link_to 'searching', textbooks_search_path %> for your books.
  </p>
  <% if logged_in? == false %>
    <p class="double new_link">
      <%= link_to 'Sign up here!', signup_path %><br/><br/>

      &nbsp;&nbsp;or
      <%= link_to "Sign in", signin_path %>
    </p>
    <p class="double">
       <%= link_to 'Search for your books', textbooks_search_path %>
    </p>
  <% end %>
  <p>
    View our site's privacy policy <%= link_to 'here', privacy_policy_path %>
  </p>
</div>
